WALL SUN SUN
Wall Sun Sun is a 9-piece band formed by songwriter and composer, Joel Cox.

The musicians in Wall Sun Sun use the basic elements of nylon-string guitars, percussion and nine part vocal harmonies to create pop music with warmth and simplicity.

The name of the project is derived from an unproved mathematical conjecture -  the so-called Wall-Sun-Sun prime numbers. It is conjectured that there are an infinite amount of these in existence, but none have yet been found.
